question: What will be the closing yield of the US 10-Year Treasury Note on Jan 30, 2026?
description: Predict the closing yield of the 10-Year T-Note on the final trading day of January 2026.
resolutionCriteria:
Resolves to the '10 Yr' rate from the 'Daily Treasury Par Yield Curve Rates' table.
- Date: Jan 30, 2026.
- Hard Lock: 3:45 PM ET (15 mins before market close).
- Fallback: If Treasury site is down, wait 24h.
